<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
 <head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="Generator" content="EditPlus®">
  <meta name="Author" content="">
  <meta name="Keywords" content="">
  <meta name="Description" content="">
  <title>Document</title>
 </head>
 <body>
  <form name="form1 method="post" action="nothingcgi">
  ID : <input type="text" name="id" value="id" readonly="readonly">읽기전용
  <br>
  Password : <input type="password" name="pw" disabled="disabled">비활성화
  <br>
  placeholder : <input type="text" name="id" value="" placeholder="닉네임">
  <br>
  남기고 싶은 글<br>
  <textarea cols="30" rows="3" name="content"></textarea>
  <br>
  당신의 성별은?[라디오버튼 이름이 같으면 하나만 선택 실제로 전송 value]<br>
  <input type="radio" name="sex" value="male" checked="chechked">남자
  <input type="radio" name="sex" value="female" id="female"> <label for="female">여자</label>해당레이블은 id femal을 위해 존재

	<br>
  취미<br>
  <input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="독서"> 독서
  <input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="여행"> 여행
  <input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="음악감상"> 음악감상
  <input type="checkbox" name="hobby" value="영화" title="말풍선"> 영화
  <br>
  당신이 구매하고 싶은 차종은?[dropdown]
  <br>
  <select name="car">
  <option value="sonata">소나타</option>
  <option value="에쿠스">에쿠스</option>
  <option value="아반떼">아반떼</option>
  </select>
  <br>
  당신이 구매하고 싶은 차종은? [list]
  <br>
  <select name="car" size="3" multiple="multiple">
  <option value="sonata">소나타</option>
  <option value="에쿠스">에쿠스</option>
  <option value="아반떼">아반떼</option>
  </select>

  <input type="hidden" name="start" value="1">
	<br>
  <input type="file" name="upload">
	<br>
	<input type="submit" value="글쓰기">
	<br>
	<input type="reset" value="취소">
	<br>
	<input type="button" value="됨?" onclick="clickButton()">

  </form>
	
	<script>
		function clickButton(){
			alert("됨");
		}
	</script>
 </body>
</html>

readonly 전송가능 disabled 전송불가
value속성에 한글적지마라 소나타 =>sonata
form안에있는 내용을 전송하는 것 submit
